\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Cross-referencing: There is no support for cross-referencing.
 If LyX finds an entry containing the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

|see\SpecialChar \ldots{}

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

